			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I was wondering why we still have the this nerf in place or the change to &quot;working as intended&quot;.    The reason extended range was nerfed on determinal spells was because of AE kiting which has been nerfed to such a state this is a nonissue now.   
<br />

<br />
Why can't we have a percent increase on lull, mez, and chant range, even the AE kiting range could be benefical for raids where you need to kite multple mobs.    We have a complete lack of focus effects, and most of our improvements are accomplished though gear and AA's.    I can't think of one good reason why this shouldn't be changed back to its orignal state.   
<br />

<br />
What do you guys think?
<br />

<br />
If this has been discussed before I apologize I didn't see a post about it.</span></td>
