				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Exended Notes(Benefical  spells only nerf)<a name="67042"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 15 04 11:14 AM</span></td>
