				<td colspan="2"><span>You keep using that word 'nerf.'
<br />

<br />
Let me point out that the original description from day one on Extended Notes has been beneficial spells only.  It was never, ever, ever intended or announced to include detrimental spells so the fact that it affected AE DoTs/debuffs always was and always will be counter to the intended, advertised purpose of the AA.  They didn't 'nerf' it to keep you from using AE to kite, they 'nerfed' it to make it do what it was always intended to do from day one.</span></td>
